headline: A Look at Bio-Techne (TECH) Valuation as Investor Interest Grows After SITC 2025 Data and Q3 Earnings Anticipation
summary: Bio-Techne (TECH) is catching eyes ahead of its upcoming quarterly earnings, with recent buzz fueled by strong clinical data at SITC 2025 and the debut of new spatial biology tools. These developments highlight the company’s expanding footprint in immuno-oncology research. See our latest analysis for Bio-Techne.
